ish-speaking world, mostly among immigrants from Germanic countries."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Otton de Fézensac was born in 1009, in Venables, Eure, Upper Normandy, France as the son of Count William of Fezensac. He married Adelaide di Susa before 1028, in France. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter. He died in 1048, in his hometown, at the age of 39."},"et":{"1009–1048":"1009–1048","1014–1091":"1014–1091","1028–1057":"1028–1057","0960–1024":"0960–1024","before 1028":"enne 1028","1091":"1091","1028":"1028","1048":"1048","0960":"0960","1014":"1014","1024":"1024","1057":"1057","1009":"1009","Venables, Eure, Upper Normandy, France":"Venables, Eure, Haute-Normandie, Prantsusmaa","Venables, Normandie, France":"Normandie, Prantsusmaa","France":"Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"1009–1048":"1009–1048","1014–1091":"1014–1091","1028–1057":"1028–1057","0960–1024":"0960–1024","before 1028":"ennen vuotta 1028","1091":"1091","1028":"1028","1048":"1048","0960":"0960","1014":"1014","1024":"1024","1057":"1057","1009":"1009","Venables, Eure, Upper Normandy, France":"Venables, Eure, Haute-Normandie, Ranska","Venables, Normandie, France":"Normandie, Ranska","France":"Ranska"},"fr":{"1009–1048":"1009–1048","1014–1091":"1014–1091","1028–1057":"1028–1057","0960–1024":"0960–1024","before 1028":"avant 1028","1091":"1091","1028":"1028","1048":"1048","0960":"0960","1014":"1014","1024":"1024","1057":"1057","1009":"1009","Venables, Eure, Upper Normandy, France":"Venables, Eure, Haute-Normandie, France","Venables, Normandie, France":"Normandie, France","France":"France","lifeSummary":"Otton de Fézensac est né en 1009, à Venables, Eure, Haute-Normandie, France, fils de Count William of Fezensac. Il a épousé Adelaide di Susa avant 1028, à France. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fille. Il est décédé en 1048, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 39 ans."},"de":{"1009–1048":"1009–1048","1014–1091":"1014–1091","1028–1057":"1028–1057","0960–1024":"0960–1024","before 1028":"vor 1028","1091":"1091","1028":"1028",